1.1.name: wordpress/technotag
1.1.description: Allows Technorati tags within <tag> </tag>. Use <tag word="tag word"> to use a different tag word than what's between the tags. Will also allow adding 'ttag' custom values for the post for listing at the end of each post and/or 'ttaglist' of comma seperated words.
